T02D2751:132a-0: @132a * // 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs mar me sbar ba la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2751:132a-2: 'jig rten sgron ma sgron ma'i dbus //
T02D2751:132a-3: zhes 'byung ba'i sgrub thabs bshad pa'o //
T02D2751:132a-4: sngags las skyes pa'i 'jig rten mgon //
T02D2751:132a-6: dges dgus rol bar bzhugs pa ni //
T02D2751:132a-7: mar mes mun pa sel ba bzhin //
T02D2751:132a-8: nyi ma'i 'od zer nub gyur cing ;
T02D2751:132a-9: / zla ba nya bar ma gyur pa'i //
T02D2751:132a-10: mtshan mo mun pa thibs po la //
T02D2751:132a-11: bsod nams bsdus pa'i mar me 'bar //
T02D2751:132a-12: rdo rje thal sbyor gsang sngags kyis //
T02D2751:132a-13: btab pa'i rtsi mar sna tshogs pa //
T02D2751:132a-14: sgron shing me lces bzhu byas la //
T02D2751:132a-15: snod bzangs padmos mtshan pa yi //
T02D2751:132a-16: kong bu shin tu byi dor byas //
T02D2751:132a-18: khyim blangs ras kyi sdong bu la //
T02D2751:132a-19: mgar gyi so ma la mes bsregs bya //
T02D2751:132b-0: sgron @132b ma'i dbus bzhugs hr'i: sa mtshan pa //
T02D2751:132b-1: sgeg po gzhon nu rol pa'i tshul //
T02D2751:132b-3: rol bzhi pa ni rnam par bsgom //
T02D2751:132b-4: de la me tog spos mchog sogs //
T02D2751:132b-5: sna tshogs mchod pa kun gyis mchod //
T02D2751:132b-6: 'jungs pa rnams dang dbul phongs dang //
T02D2751:132b-7: sdig ldan rgyal po'i mar dkar sbyin //
T02D2751:132b-8: tshangs pa'i gnas bzhi nyer brtsams pa'i //
T02D2751:132b-9: chos sbyin rjes su yid byed dang //
T02D2751:132b-10: snying po'i rnal 'byor mchog sdor bcas //
T02D2751:132b-11: thun gsum du ni rtag tu bya //
T02D2751:132b-12: bdun phrag bdun gyi cho ga yis //
T02D2751:132b-13: tho rangs mtshan ma gsum mthong ba //
T02D2751:132b-14: de tshe gzhon nu gzhon nu ma'i //
T02D2751:132b-15: ston mo byin la me tog gi //
T02D2751:132b-16: phreng bas mgul brgyan me long dang //
T02D2751:132b-17: mar me'i 'khor yug dri byug dang ;
T02D2751:132b-18: / mandal rol mo phul nas ni //
T02D2751:132b-19: mar me'i du ba'i thig le sbyin //
T02D2751:132b-20: de la sngags ni 'di yin te /
T02D2751:132b-21: aa ka ru yi bdug pas bdugs /
T02D2751:132b-22: aom a'a: hr'i: a'a ry'a ba lo ke te a'a
T02D2751:132b-23: lo ka dzny'a na dzva la dzva la pra kaspa
T02D2751:132b-24: ma ma tsitte sth'i ra h'um h'um h'um /
T02D2751:132b-25: rang lus mar me 'bar ba dang ;
T02D2751:132b-26: / mkha' la lha mthong lung bstan pa'o //
